30005594@@@@@@It is a waterproof product and rechargeable DC batteries will be used, allowing unrestricted placement of the bin.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:198; ntucle-sid:1353@LMC@2019-06-15
30005595@@@@@@Motor will be modified by size and power, sized at 5cm in width and 10cm in height, to implement in the bin.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:198; ntucle-sid:1354@LMC@2019-06-15
30005596@@@@@@[2] Position sensor will be used to detect when the rubbish is full.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:198; ntucle-sid:1355@LMC@2019-06-15
30005597@@@@@@[3, 4] An ultrasonic transducer will be installed in each bin to send a wave signal to the cleaner when it detects the bin is full.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:198; ntucle-sid:1356@LMC@2019-06-15
30005598@@@@@@[5]@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:198; ntucle-sid:1357@LMC@2019-06-15
