30005625@@@@@@SLEEP TRACKING DEVICE@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1548@LMC@2019-06-15
30005626@@@@@@Name :@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1549@LMC@2019-06-15
30005627@@@@@@Matriculation No.@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1551@LMC@2019-06-15
30005628@@@@@@:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1552@LMC@2019-06-15
30005629@@@@@@School :@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1554@LMC@2019-06-15
30005630@@@@@@Group :@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1556@LMC@2019-06-15
30005631@@@@@@Tutor :@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1558@LMC@2019-06-15
30005632@@@@@@Date of submission :@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1560@LMC@2019-06-15
30005633@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1562@LMC@2019-06-15
30005634@@@@@@Many people wake up feeling drowsy even though they had enough sleep.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1563@LMC@2019-06-15
30005635@@@@@@It affects their productivity for the rest of the day.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1564@LMC@2019-06-15
30005636@@@@@@This is due to an unfinished sleep cycle.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1565@LMC@2019-06-15
30005637@@@@@@When people are asleep, they experience several cycles of sleep [1].@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1566@LMC@2019-06-15
30005638@@@@@@By controlling their sleep cycle, people can improve their sleep quality and wake up refreshed [2].@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1567@LMC@2019-06-15
30005639@@@@@@A recent research has shown that people could track our sleep cycle by observing their own sound and movement when they are asleep [3].@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1568@LMC@2019-06-15
30005640@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1569@LMC@2019-06-15
30005641@@@@@@Today, there is already an application for smartphones that can track body movements when someone is asleep.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1570@LMC@2019-06-15
30005642@@@@@@However, this application still have many downsides.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1571@LMC@2019-06-15
30005643@@@@@@It is not very practical since the user has to charge the phone when the application is being used.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1572@LMC@2019-06-15
30005644@@@@@@The user may also damage the phone by accidentally knock the phone out of the bed.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1573@LMC@2019-06-15
30005645@@@@@@Therefore, a simpler device that can do the same thing needs to be developed.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1574@LMC@2019-06-15
30005646@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1575@LMC@2019-06-15
30005647@@@@@@The objective of this proposal is to make a device that is more convenient to use than the smartphone application.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1576@LMC@2019-06-15
30005648@@@@@@The form of the product is like a pebble and it uses accelerometer to identify movements.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1577@LMC@2019-06-15
30005649@@@@@@The user can put it near him when he is asleep without noticing it.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1578@LMC@2019-06-15
30005650@@@@@@The design is waterproof and shock resistant.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1579@LMC@2019-06-15
30005651@@@@@@The device consumes low energy and is able to operate for more than 30 hours.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1580@LMC@2019-06-15
30005652@@@@@@This device will also be developed along with a website and an application for smartphones.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1581@LMC@2019-06-15
30005653@@@@@@After the sleep cycle is identified, the application will calculate the range of time that is most suitable to ring the alarm.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1582@LMC@2019-06-15
30005654@@@@@@Benefits­­@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1583@LMC@2019-06-15
30005655@@@@@@This sleep tracking device is an advanced version of the sleep tracking application on smartphones.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1584@LMC@2019-06-15
30005656@@@@@@It is more practical and safe to use.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1585@LMC@2019-06-15
30005657@@@@@@By using this device, the user can identify his sleep cycle and have the alarm set at the time when his sleep cycle ends.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1586@LMC@2019-06-15
30005658@@@@@@This leads to a refreshed feeling and improved productivity throughout the day.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1587@LMC@2019-06-15
30005659@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1588@LMC@2019-06-15
30005660@@@@@@In order to develop the product, these steps will be carried out:@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1589@LMC@2019-06-15
30005661@@@@@@1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1590@LMC@2019-06-15
30005662@@@@@@Develop the website and the application with SleepBot, an existing company that has previously made the smartphone application.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1591@LMC@2019-06-15
30005663@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1592@LMC@2019-06-15
30005664@@@@@@Cooperate with Pirate3D to design the product.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1593@LMC@2019-06-15
