30005675@@@@@@Conclusion@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1604@LMC@2019-06-15
30005676@@@@@@Many people experience drowsiness when waking up.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1605@LMC@2019-06-15
30005677@@@@@@It reduces their productivity for the rest of the day.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:199; ntucle-sid:1606@LMC@2019-06-15
