30005682@@@@@@Background:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1398@LMC@2019-06-15
30005683@@@@@@Getting around campus has been a common problem for NTU students.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1399@LMC@2019-06-15
30005684@@@@@@Even with the existing transportation arrangements available within campus (public buses and campus shuttle bus services), there are still criticism towards the consistency and effectiveness of these services.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1400@LMC@2019-06-15
30005685@@@@@@According to demographics provided by NTU (Nanyang Technological University, 2015), faculty/staff members and undergraduate population hit record highs of 7004 and 23,713 respectively in the year 2014-2015.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1401@LMC@2019-06-15
30005686@@@@@@This is a worrying trend for NTU as an increasing population will exacerbate the issue at hand.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1402@LMC@2019-06-15
30005687@@@@@@As such, it is crucial to look into alternative means of transportation to accommodate the higher human traffic within campus.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1403@LMC@2019-06-15
30005688@@@@@@Problem:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1404@LMC@2019-06-15
30005689@@@@@@NTU is a huge campus and getting around can be very tiring, especially from the academic blocks to the residential halls or Sports and Recreational Complex.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1405@LMC@2019-06-15
30005690@@@@@@NTU provides shuttle buses that goes around in loops, operating from 0800-2300H daily.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1406@LMC@2019-06-15
30005691@@@@@@However, the frequencies are often irregular and unpredictable during non-peak hours; and during peak hours, boarding the bus can be difficult, especially for the more populated bus stops.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1407@LMC@2019-06-15
30005692@@@@@@As such, individuals are forced to cater in a larger buffer time when getting around.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1408@LMC@2019-06-15
30005693@@@@@@Solution:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1409@LMC@2019-06-15
30005694@@@@@@The main goal of this proposal is to introduce an alternative option for people to get around NTU, in addition to buses.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1410@LMC@2019-06-15
30005695@@@@@@NTU Bike-Share is a model where bicycle rental terminals will be strategically placed throughout campus.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1411@LMC@2019-06-15
30005696@@@@@@Users will select their rental option (day-hire/distance hire) on the bike-share computer available at every terminal and make payment via their ez-link at the card reader mounted beside the computer.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1412@LMC@2019-06-15
30005697@@@@@@Once payment has been approved, the locking mechanism will deactivate for the selected bike hired.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1413@LMC@2019-06-15
30005698@@@@@@Benefits:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1414@LMC@2019-06-15
30005699@@@@@@With NTU Bike-Share, users are able to plan their travel time better as they do not have to factor in as much buffer time.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1415@LMC@2019-06-15
30005700@@@@@@Additionally, it provides users waiting for buses an assurance from being late as they always have a second option available if the bus service is inconsistent.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1416@LMC@2019-06-15
30005701@@@@@@Moreover, it is an eco-friendly and healthy initiative, which aligns with NTU’s goal of going green.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1417@LMC@2019-06-15
30005702@@@@@@Implementation:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1418@LMC@2019-06-15
30005703@@@@@@1) Study case studies and learn from experts who has implemented the bike-share system (eg.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1419@LMC@2019-06-15
30005704@@@@@@Melbourne Bike Share, Skidmore College) to understand the strengths and weaknesses of each model, before choosing the most appropriate bike-share model to adopt in NTU@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1420@LMC@2019-06-15
30005705@@@@@@2) Collaborate with “Onbikeshare” (Onbikeshare, 2012), a niche manufacturer based in the United States with expertise in custom made bike sharing systems.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1421@LMC@2019-06-15
30005706@@@@@@Purchase customized bicycles, bike racks, locking system and software from them.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1422@LMC@2019-06-15
30005707@@@@@@3) Establish the registration process with NTU the student services center such that students and staff can adopt the new initiative seamlessly once operational.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1423@LMC@2019-06-15
