30005715@@@@@@Conclusion:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1431@LMC@2019-06-15
30005716@@@@@@NTU is still a long way from having a laudable transportation infrastructure within campus.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1432@LMC@2019-06-15
