30005718@@@@@@The proposed NTU Bike-Share model aims to improve the current situation by providing alternative means for people to get around campus and mitigate the common frustrations expressed on the ground.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:201; ntucle-sid:1434@LMC@2019-06-15
30005719@@@@@@Title@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1529@LMC@2019-06-15
30005720@@@@@@Thermo-regulator of the Era@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1530@LMC@2019-06-15
30005721@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1531@LMC@2019-06-15
30005722@@@@@@Air conditioner is an electric appliance that alternate surrounding temperature.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1532@LMC@2019-06-15
30005723@@@@@@Nowadays, portable air conditioners are getting ubiquitous due to the easement provided by them.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1533@LMC@2019-06-15
30005724@@@@@@Portable air conditioners can be carried from one place to another.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1534@LMC@2019-06-15
30005725@@@@@@There is no troublesome installation procedure as well.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1535@LMC@2019-06-15
30005726@@@@@@Portable air conditioners function alike to the traditional air conditionals.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1536@LMC@2019-06-15
30005727@@@@@@They absorb the air in the room, cooling it and then release it back to the room.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1537@LMC@2019-06-15
30005728@@@@@@Meanwhile, the hot air produced in this process is channeled away from the house through a hose [1].@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1538@LMC@2019-06-15
30005729@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1539@LMC@2019-06-15
30005730@@@@@@Portable air conditioners have to be placed near a window as they have to release the hot air away from the room.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1540@LMC@2019-06-15
30005731@@@@@@Therefore, they are not feasible to be placed in enclosed rooms.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1541@LMC@2019-06-15
30005732@@@@@@Moving a portable air conditioner from one place to another is harder than it sounds as the ventilation system including the hose and the plate installed in the window have to be transferred together as well.@@@@1@36@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1542@LMC@2019-06-15
30005733@@@@@@Besides, portable air conditioners need a continuous power source to function.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1543@LMC@2019-06-15
30005734@@@@@@They cannot be used in open areas.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1544@LMC@2019-06-15
30005735@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:202; ntucle-sid:1545@LMC@2019-06-15
