30005921@@@@@@MozzieAway Container (MAC)@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1622@LMC@2019-06-15
30005922@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1623@LMC@2019-06-15
30005923@@@@@@MozzieAway Container (MAC)@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1624@LMC@2019-06-15
30005924@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1625@LMC@2019-06-15
30005925@@@@@@Mosquitoes are a menace to everyone and they are known to be the number one killer in the world by transmitting various types of diseases such as malaria and dengue.@@@@1@30@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1626@LMC@2019-06-15
30005926@@@@@@According to World Health Organisation, malaria has killed over 725000 people annually.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1627@LMC@2019-06-15
30005927@@@@@@[1] Their larvae are commonly found in places with stagnant water such as containers and drains.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1628@LMC@2019-06-15
30005928@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1629@LMC@2019-06-15
30005929@@@@@@As a country with a tropical climate, the combination of a warm and wet weather in Singapore provides a good breeding ground for the mosquitoes.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1630@LMC@2019-06-15
30005930@@@@@@According to NEA, the most common breeding ground for mosquitoes are domestic containers[2].@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1631@LMC@2019-06-15
30005931@@@@@@These containers are used for everyday activities such as watering the plants and may contain residue water, thus promoting the growth of mosquitoes’ larvae.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1632@LMC@2019-06-15
30005932@@@@@@Therefore, in order to reduce their breeding areas, measures are needed to remove residue water found in these containers.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1633@LMC@2019-06-15
30005933@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1634@LMC@2019-06-15
30005934@@@@@@The 100mm x 220mm MAC proposed will be double-layered with the ability to displace residue water while hindering the growth of larvae.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1635@LMC@2019-06-15
30005935@@@@@@The main material will be plastic as it is economically efficient and durable[3].@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1636@LMC@2019-06-15
30005936@@@@@@The main feature is that at the lower portion of the MAC, a CO2 mixer will be fitted.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1637@LMC@2019-06-15
30005937@@@@@@Mosquitoes are known to be attracted to heat and carbon dioxide [4]; as such the possibility of enticing the mosquitoes to breed will be higher.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1638@LMC@2019-06-15
30005938@@@@@@The main ingredients of the co2 mixer will consist of sugar and yeast which will result in fermentation.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1639@LMC@2019-06-15
30005939@@@@@@The fermentation process will produce CO2 which will seep through the first layer.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1640@LMC@2019-06-15
30005940@@@@@@The secondary feature is when it holds a certain amount of water, the first layer will tilt at an angle and subsequently remove all the water inside.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1641@LMC@2019-06-15
30005941@@@@@@The container will have a locking mechanism on the first layer to lock it in place should it be needed for water transportation.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1642@LMC@2019-06-15
30005942@@@@@@Not only that, it also comprises a detachable second layer for the user to get rid of the larvae.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1643@LMC@2019-06-15
30005943@@@@@@Benefit@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1644@LMC@2019-06-15
30005944@@@@@@Firstly, the MAC is quite user-friendly and allows for automatic removal of residue water.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1645@LMC@2019-06-15
30005945@@@@@@Not only that, it can be used as a reusable mosquito trap while still retaining its ability for water storage.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1646@LMC@2019-06-15
30005946@@@@@@Furthermore, the component used for the co2 mixer are easily available household items which will be convenient for the users.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1647@LMC@2019-06-15
30005947@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1648@LMC@2019-06-15
30005948@@@@@@The MAC will be developed with the following steps:@@@@1@9@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1649@LMC@2019-06-15
30005949@@@@@@1@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1650@LMC@2019-06-15
30005950@@@@@@Conducting experiments to discover the optimum level of the fermentation process and exactly how much water is needed to tilt the first layer of the container.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1651@LMC@2019-06-15
30005951@@@@@@2@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1652@LMC@2019-06-15
30005952@@@@@@Engaging material engineers from DUPONT to pinpoint a suitable material for the CO2 to seep through the first layer and to construct a good built-in CO2 mixer.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1653@LMC@2019-06-15
30005953@@@@@@Cost/Budget@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1654@LMC@2019-06-15
30005954@@@@@@CO2 mixer $10@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1655@LMC@2019-06-15
30005955@@@@@@Waterproofing spray $20@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1656@LMC@2019-06-15
30005956@@@@@@Container $5@@@@1@2@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1657@LMC@2019-06-15
30005957@@@@@@Conclusion@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1658@LMC@2019-06-15
30005958@@@@@@In conclusion, the health threat of the mosquito borne diseases cannot be underestimated.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1659@LMC@2019-06-15
30005959@@@@@@The MAC is a cost-effective solution to address this problem by preventing mosquitoes from breeding and still retaining its use.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:207; ntucle-sid:1660@LMC@2019-06-15
