30006078@@@@@@However, using a simple mask causes another problem.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1457@LMC@2019-06-15
30006079@@@@@@Masks are disposable, using them creates a lot of waste.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1458@LMC@2019-06-15
30006080@@@@@@High-end technological devices are very effective in purifying air, but they are very costly.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1459@LMC@2019-06-15
30006081@@@@@@Hence, a new air purifying device which is affordable, compact and efficient is needed.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1460@LMC@2019-06-15
30006082@@@@@@Solution:@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1461@LMC@2019-06-15
30006083@@@@@@The main idea is to propose an air purifier which is affordable, compact and highly efficient.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1462@LMC@2019-06-15
30006084@@@@@@This device has a dimension of 20cm x 30 cm x 2.5cm.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1463@LMC@2019-06-15
30006085@@@@@@It’s a rectangle device, with its largest surface about the size of A4 paper.@@@@1@14@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1464@LMC@2019-06-15
30006086@@@@@@This A4 paper sized air purifier has 4 rubber suction cups that allow it to be mounted on window, where the air enter our house.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1465@LMC@2019-06-15
30006087@@@@@@On the side which it mounts on the window there will be a solar panel, which is the secondary energy source of this device.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1466@LMC@2019-06-15
30006088@@@@@@Its primary source is batteries or plug in.@@@@1@8@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1467@LMC@2019-06-15
30006089@@@@@@It sucks air from 4 sides and expel clean air into the house.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1468@LMC@2019-06-15
30006090@@@@@@The internal filter is pleated cotton filters, this type of filter has more surface area than normal single sheet filter, thus increasing its efficiency.@@@@1@24@ntucle-docid:213; ntucle-sid:1469@LMC@2019-06-15
