30006311@@@@@@EZ-Park, easy ride@@@@1@3@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1701@LMC@2019-06-15
30006312@@@@@@Background@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1702@LMC@2019-06-15
30006313@@@@@@For many people living in first-world countries, their means of travelling from place to place is by car.@@@@1@18@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1703@LMC@2019-06-15
30006314@@@@@@The four-wheeled automobile is a convenient and comfortable form of transportation.@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1704@LMC@2019-06-15
30006315@@@@@@However, being the owner of a car also comes with its own set of problems.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1705@LMC@2019-06-15
30006316@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1706@LMC@2019-06-15
30006317@@@@@@When one drives a car, he/she also needs a place to park the car when they reach their destination.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1707@LMC@2019-06-15
30006318@@@@@@However, the fact that land is a limited resource and the general investment of land for more lucrative purposes means there is generally insufficient carparks and parking spaces.@@@@1@28@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1708@LMC@2019-06-15
30006319@@@@@@This problem is very apparent in Singapore (Barter, 2011, pp.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1709@LMC@2019-06-15
30006320@@@@@@14,15,16) and wastes the time of drivers all around (Shoup, 2007).@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1710@LMC@2019-06-15
30006321@@@@@@Fortunately, this problem can be alleviated with the help of technology@@@@1@11@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1711@LMC@2019-06-15
30006322@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1712@LMC@2019-06-15
30006323@@@@@@The creation of EZ-Park sought to address this problem by providing real time information on available parking spaces in carparks.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1713@LMC@2019-06-15
30006324@@@@@@Sensors will be embedded in each parking space as well as around the whole carpark, recreating a 3D image of the entire carpark inside a smartphone application.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1714@LMC@2019-06-15
30006325@@@@@@Data on carparks and their available parking spaces and its images will be updated real-time every minute to indicate any available lots and their respective locations, with a simple colour coding of red for occupied lots, green for available ones, and the number of waiting cars.@@@@1@46@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1715@LMC@2019-06-15
30006326@@@@@@This is possible as when drivers enter the carpark, they are recommended to indicate on the application that they’re looking for a parking space and likewise indicate when they have found a parking space.@@@@1@34@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1716@LMC@2019-06-15
30006327@@@@@@EZ-Park can also suggest alternative carparks nearby with more available parking spaces if a particular carpark has a lot of waiting cars.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1717@LMC@2019-06-15
30006328@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1718@LMC@2019-06-15
30006329@@@@@@EZ-Park makes the lives of drivers easier as they know exactly where to drive towards in the carpark to get their parking space.@@@@1@23@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1719@LMC@2019-06-15
30006330@@@@@@This saves their time and frustration from waiting for a parking space.@@@@1@12@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1720@LMC@2019-06-15
30006331@@@@@@It is also more convenient for drivers in the sense that they can plan their journey in advance by checking the carparks’ available spaces beforehand and then choosing a carpark to park at based on their own informed judgement.@@@@1@39@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1721@LMC@2019-06-15
30006332@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1722@LMC@2019-06-15
30006333@@@@@@The following steps are taken to create the EZ-Park application:@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1723@LMC@2019-06-15
30006334@@@@@@Sensors created by a software company will be installed by the proper authorities at various major carparks island-wide, in each parking space and around the carpark complex.@@@@1@27@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1724@LMC@2019-06-15
30006335@@@@@@The application, EZ-Park will be created by an IT company, which will synchronise the installed sensors in the carpark with the application database in collaboration with the software company.@@@@1@29@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1725@LMC@2019-06-15
30006336@@@@@@Tests will be conducted to ensure the functionality of EZ-Park.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1726@LMC@2019-06-15
30006337@@@@@@EZ-Park will be monitored at a designated headquarters office (HQ), whereby key user information is transmitted to and processed by EZ-Park personnel.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:218; ntucle-sid:1727@LMC@2019-06-15
