30006354@@@@@@In preparation for the increase in demand, the government is utilizing Information Communication Technology (ICT) in managing patients’ medical records, facilitating communication and allowing the patients to perform self-monitoring (IDA, 2015).@@@@1@31@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1754@LMC@2019-06-15
30006355@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1755@LMC@2019-06-15
