30006362@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1762@LMC@2019-06-15
30006363@@@@@@With health in mind, an elderly-friendly smart phone called “Santé” (French word for health) will be produced.@@@@1@17@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1763@LMC@2019-06-15
30006364@@@@@@Its dimension will be 12 cm by 6 cm and 0.5 cm thick.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1764@LMC@2019-06-15
30006365@@@@@@The design of the product will be determined after the research and development.@@@@1@13@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1765@LMC@2019-06-15
30006366@@@@@@“Santé” will have touch screen user interface (UI) that is optimized for the elderly users.@@@@1@15@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1766@LMC@2019-06-15
30006367@@@@@@Benefits@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:220; ntucle-sid:1767@LMC@2019-06-15
