30006428@@@@@@Never be Late Again@@@@1@4@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1624@LMC@2019-06-15
30006429@@@@@@Problem@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1625@LMC@2019-06-15
30006430@@@@@@Students in NTU who have classes back to back, with each class several distance away from each other tend to take time to reach and miss the first 10-15 minutes of the next class.@@@@1@34@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1626@LMC@2019-06-15
30006431@@@@@@Being late is also not very conventional and it does not make a good first impression.@@@@1@16@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1627@LMC@2019-06-15
30006432@@@@@@This occurs mainly because the classes might be held in different areas of the school and by the time students reach the next class, they miss the lecture time where lecturers might have stated the importance and objectives of the topic being tested in an upcoming test.@@@@1@47@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1628@LMC@2019-06-15
30006433@@@@@@Or sometimes when the tutor goes through the questions you may miss out and not know how to do.@@@@1@19@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1629@LMC@2019-06-15
30006434@@@@@@This is a major problem for students in NTU especially for freshman in the first few months where they take a little more time to navigate their way to each class and find the shortest possible way to reach on time.@@@@1@41@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1630@LMC@2019-06-15
30006435@@@@@@Solution@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1631@LMC@2019-06-15
30006436@@@@@@NTU can provide a service to students where they can rent a two wheel self-balancing scooter or unicycle that has now become very trendy and popular.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1632@LMC@2019-06-15
30006437@@@@@@This new scooter designed is portable and is very efficient.@@@@1@10@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1633@LMC@2019-06-15
30006438@@@@@@Students can probably rent it for a day at the service center for a price and use it around the school for an entire day.@@@@1@25@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1634@LMC@2019-06-15
30006439@@@@@@A deposit charge will be collected together with details and matriculation card of the students, but it will be returned back when the student gives it back at the end of the day.@@@@1@33@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1635@LMC@2019-06-15
30006440@@@@@@This way, students can travel all the around NTU faster and safer, without missing any important lecture and tutorials by arriving late.@@@@1@22@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1636@LMC@2019-06-15
30006441@@@@@@It is fast, efficient and trendy too.@@@@1@7@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1637@LMC@2019-06-15
30006442@@@@@@Benefit@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1638@LMC@2019-06-15
30006443@@@@@@This will definitely benefit students who are always late due to their previous lesson at another corner of the school.@@@@1@20@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1639@LMC@2019-06-15
30006444@@@@@@Moreover, being late will never be a problem because this two wheel scooter helps to reach their next class destination in a shorter period of time.@@@@1@26@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1640@LMC@2019-06-15
30006445@@@@@@Implementation@@@@1@1@ntucle-docid:223; ntucle-sid:1641@LMC@2019-06-15
